    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "っ……あのガキ……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That brat…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 6.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん！？　抑えて！　抑えて下さい……！\n周りに大勢いますから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san!? Hold back! Please hold back…!\nThere are a lot of people around…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.2666669209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ふざっけんな、あのガキ……！\nこっちが大人な対応してりゃあ調子に乗りやがって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't mess with me‚ that brat…!\nThe moment I act mature‚ she starts getting cocky!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんみたいな口調になってますよ！？\nお願いですから落ち着いて下さい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're starting to sound like kana!?\nPlease‚ please calm down…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7552992943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "誰がkanaみたいですって……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who's like kana…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ダメだ、埒が明かない！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is no good‚ I'm getting nowhere!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今の演技指示の理由を聞いて来ますから！\nfranさんは待ってて下さい！　ね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll go ask about the reason for that acting direction!\nPlease wait here‚ fran-san! Okay!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0999997457,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5699.9997458,
          "startTime": 33.6333330791
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.1666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅん。私の泳ぎがとっても画面映えするから\nどこかで入れたいって訳ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm. Because my swimming looks really good on screen‚\nshe wants to include it somewhere‚ is that it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "以前の生放送番組での対決企画の時\nfranさんは相当練習を積んで泳ぎましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back during that live broadcast competition‚\nyou practiced really hard at swimming‚ didn’t you‚ fran-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどね、あの時の泳ぎを覚えてた……と\nまぁ、着眼点は悪くないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so she remembered my swimming from that time…\nWell‚ that's not a bad observation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "どっちにしろ、このタイミングで泳ぐ意味は\n全然分かんないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Either way‚ I still don't see the point of swimming\nat a time like this‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5044254836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "しょうがない、やってやるわよ\n全力でやってやるから、ちゃんと撮っときなさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be helped‚ I'll do it.\nI'll give it my all‚ so make sure you film it properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1666664124,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4729.455947799991,
          "startTime": 69.8961223602
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah‚ hah‚ hah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7000091553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（これまで散々働いた後に全力で泳いだから……）\n（さすがに疲れてるみたいだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Since she swam with full effort after working so hard…）\n（She seems to be quite tired.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、お疲れ様です\n手、貸しますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ fran-san.\nLet me give you a hand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "はい？　そんなの別に……いや、そうね\n助かります……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? That's not really… no‚ you're right.\nThat helps… hah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、もう、疲れた……\n久しぶりだからほんっと疲れた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah~ geez‚ I'm tired…\nIt's been a while‚ so I'm really tired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5000048321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.9000048321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、何が楽しくてナイトプールで\n全力で泳がなきゃいけないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ why do I have to swim with my full effort in a night pool?\nWhat’s fun about that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3333381654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、こんだけ体を張ってあげたんだし\nどこかで使うでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I put my body on the line this much‚\nso she'll use it somewhere‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6947177251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あれだけハードに動き回ってたのに、泳ぎも全力で……\nfranさんはアイドルの鑑ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after moving around that hard‚ you also swam with full effort…\nYou're a model idol‚ fran-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.3000086467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "周りが無駄に盛り上がってるのが、腹立ちますけどね\nこういうノリ、苦手なのに……くしゅん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's annoying how everyone around is getting unnecessarily excited.\nI'm not good with this kind of vibe… achoo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1666714987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "う～……早く撤収しましょ\nはぁ～、やっと帰れる～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… let's wrap up quickly.\nAhh‚ I can finally go home~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MVの公開後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the MV release",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.33334198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 141.8333381654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "franさん。新曲のMVはかなり好評ですね\n……って、ど、どうしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san. The new song's MV is quite well-received.\n…Wait‚ wh-what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1000048321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "確かにMVは好評でしたよ\n実際、よく出来てたと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The MV was indeed well-received.\nI actually think it was well made.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.9333381654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私が全力で泳がされたところがMV本編で\n一秒も使われてないのはどういうことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… the part where I was made to swim with full effort wasn't used\nfor even one second in the actual MV! What's that about!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1333381654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "それは……kanaさんがきっと、MV全体のバランス\nを見て、やむを得ずカットしたんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… kana probably looked at the overall balance of the MV\nand had to cut it out of necessity‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.3333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
